reviewText: Here I am thinking I'm purchasing Seasons 7 of Dragnet when it is nothing more than a DVD with 4 measly randomly picked episodes from the 1950s.  This is a joke and a waste of money.  Does anyone actually sell Season 7 or 1-9 of Dragnet from the 1950s?
Like it just the way it is!!!  No fancy restoration.  It's exactly like it was when it first appeared on TV.  However, for that reason, a lot of people might not like it.
No problems with Dragnet. Great show. Hate this is the last one!
Great classic  crime drama .Much better than Dragnet of the 1960s
Great memories of growing u!  I am currently listing to the old RADIO program series...
Wow! Just the facts ... super dvd collection of original TV series.
